name: .WSF File Extension
summary: Learn about .WSF files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: A WSF file is an executable script for Windows that can incorporate JScript and VBScript routines and may include XML elements. WSF files run themselves if WScript or CScript is installed.

content: Be cautious when working with unknown WSF files. Do not open them unless you can verify their integrity since they can contain viruses.
